channel.title: Where did it go? I liked that game :( !The post your clipboard game!
channel.description:
Hoping you all want to play again. I can't find the thread.
[b]The Post your Clipboard game![/b]
Here are the rules: -Click reply, then push control-v. -Do not explain anything. -Do not post anything else than what is on your clipboard. (Yes, that applies to the starter of this "game" too :rolleyes:).
Remember this game? [me=VB7 Rocks]wants to play![/me]
(Of course, don't just copy some random crap off of something stupid, it has to be what's really on your clipboard right now)
:)
